text: Mandy Debono (born 24 November 1987) is a Maltese footballer who plays as a defender for First Division club Swieqi United FC. She has been a member of the Malta women's national team. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Maltese women's footballers Category:Malta women's international footballers Category:Hibernians F.C. players
